short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Adds a window to save and manage code snippets for Webflow projects.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Codehub for Webflow help you manage your codesnippets.

THE PROBLEM: If you often find yourself searching through multiple projects to find those handy code snippets you've used before, Codehub is here to simplify your life. 

THE SOLUTION: This extension provides a centralized hub where you can save, manage, and easily access all your frequently used code snippets. With Codehub, reusing code across your Webflow projects becomes a breeze, saving you time and effort. It's the perfect tool for developers looking to optimize their coding process and enhance productivity on Webflow. Simply copy the snippets that you have saved and paste them where you need them.

Also enjoy the premade community snippets!
